{"tid":168521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"以下故事對父母教育子女有何啟發？試談談你的看法。","createTime":"2017-03-23T15:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T17:35:13.000Z","uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c65b02be5c5f79cb7511867cdea74927d5abb791","tid":168521,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"以下故事對父母教育子女有何啟發？試談談你的看法。<br />\n開學第一天，新老師步入課室，叫所有學生站立。所有學生也站著，只有一位同學仍坐著，老師便嚴厲斥責。<br />\n「你快站起來。」<br />\n「他已經站起來了。」<br />\n全班學生哄堂大笑。<span style=\"color: red;\">原來這位同學個子矮小，已經站起來，但仍像坐著</span>。老師只好連忙叫全班坐下。"},{"pid":"8e3a99cd14afe28937b26a022032dd5bfe3fb1b2","tid":168521,"uid":93932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"贏在起跑線好重要"},{"pid":"811277c90265c0c162e4f4607cbba87f7af5dccd","tid":168521,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"[red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他</span>[/red<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d13198c2b783dc53cca7c485b97146a51727aa7","tid":168521,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54095ecb4ec07b55d4b3d12f38b0d56563c30331","tid":168521,"uid":10612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"才能"},{"pid":"70764abedf7fdb085ec9fc70f84d245b6a3c3050","tid":168521,"uid":10612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係笠水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d11b1fe0dce2a5c43cfdbbb36996ad41700ac2","t